name: Frantic Again!
description: Frantic again is the third in the Frantic Frag series. It is about the same size as it's predecessor, Frantic2 however unlike Frantic2 it only has the 3 smaller weapons(shotgun, chaingun, & chainsaw). Ammo, armor, sniper spots are in plenty & there are a few secrets in this one too... Have at it Folks!!
